name: Mountain Sightings #4
description: PETEROA’S VOLCANO WAS ACTIVE FOR CENTURIES, BUT NEVER SHOWED MAGMA, UNTIL THAT DAY WHERE WE WITNESSED ONE OF THE MOST STYLISH SPACECRAFTS WE EVER SAW. RETROFUTURISTIC AESTHETIC WAS BASED ON THIS KIND OF SIGHTINGS I GUESS. DRAWING FROM MY MEMOIRES, UTER FRANCIS ÖRST
